Setup for the test case presented in Soucasse et al.(2014) article.

For more details see "Numerical study of coupled molecular gas radiation 
and natural convection in a differentially heated cubical cavity".
doi: 10.1615/ComputThermalScien.2012005118

Replace the functions present in RTS_functions.f90 with those present in user_functions.f90


To facilitate post-processing, replace these lines in the output.rts file.

!===============================================================
!                          Slices Save
!===============================================================
.true.   !on/off slices save module (only for 3D simulations)
 2        !Slicing Method: 1-Percent 2-Point 3-Node
 2        !Number of Slices
!---------------------------------------------------------------
! Axis  Percent  Point   Node    ID
   x      50     0.25d0   10      3 
   x      50     0.75d0   10      3
!<> add more lines if needed
!===============================================================
!                     Lineup Variable Save               
!===============================================================
.true.   !on/off lineup save module (only for 3D simulations)
 1        !Method: 1-Point 2-Node
 4        !Number of Lineups
!---------------------------------------------------------------!
! Axis  >>   X:(x,a,b)   Y:(a,y,b)   Z:(a,b,z)                  !
!---------------------------------------------------------------!
!             CV Point         CV Node      Variable            !
! Axis      a        b        a       b        ID               !
!---------------------------------------------------------------!
   x      0.25d0   0.25d0     10      10        3 
   x      0.25d0   0.75d0     10      10        3
   x      0.25d0   1.00d0     10      10        10
   x      0.25d0   0.00d0     10      10        10
!===============================================================
